title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 §§ 1-1.3 - Credit cards
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 §§ 1-1.3 - Credit cards

State Regulations

The term "credit cards" includes credit, bank, debit, travel and entertainment or pre-paid payment cards or products that can be
presented at a physical point-of-sale terminal, electronically, or by
telephone. Notes
